al|Tennis}}\n* {{ITF profile}}\n* {{WTA}}\n\n{{Australian Open women's doubles champions}}\n{{Wimbledon women's doubles champions}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Michel, Peggy}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:1949 births]]\n[[Category:American female tennis players]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Santa Monica, California]]\n[[Category:Tennis people from California]]\n[[Category:Grand Slam (tennis) champions in women's doubles]]\n[[Category:Australian Open (tennis) champions]]\n[[Category:Wimbledon champions]]\n\n\n{{US-tennis-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|American tennis player}}\n{{Infobox tennis biography\n| name                          = Peggy Michel\n| image                         =\n| fullname                      = Margaret Michel\n| country                       = {{USA}}\n| residence                     =\n| birth_date                    = {{birth date and age|1949|02|02}}\n| birth_place                   = Santa Monica, California\n| height                        = \n| weight                        = \n| turnedpro                     = \n| retired                       = \n| plays                         = \n| careerprizemoney              =\n| singlesrecord                 = 16\u201314\n| singlestitles                 = \n| highestsinglesranking         = \n| AustralianOpenresult          = 3R (1974, 1975)\n| FrenchOpenresult              =\n| Wimbledonresult               = 4R (1969, 1973)\n| USOpenresult                  = 3R (1969)\n| Othertournaments              = \n| MastersCupresult              = \n| WTAChampionshipsresult        = \n| Olympicssresult               = \n| doublesrecord                 = 30\u201310\n| doublestitles                 = 3\n| highestdoublesranking         =\n| grandslamsdoublesresults      = \n| AustralianOpenDoublesresult   = '''W''' (1974, 1975)\n| FrenchOpenDoublesresult       =\n| WimbledonDoublesresult        = '''W''' (1974)\n| USOpenDoublesresult           = SF (1974)\n| OthertournamentsDoubles     